# .roadmap.platform_ppi — PPI (Protein-Protein Interaction) Cross-Cutting Platform Layer

Status: WRITE-ONLY (uncommitted) — 2026-05-08
Scope: 5-axis (QUANTUM / WEAVE / VIROCAPSID / RIBOZYME / NANOBOT) cross-cutting platform — Protein-Protein Interaction modulator paradigm
Origin: 165-option brainstorm Top 5 promote (4.8/5) — historical "undruggable target" → 2020s 다수 FDA 승인 paradigm shift
Position: 4th cross-cutting platform layer (after covalent / TPD / PROTAC frame)

