## 2. 5-Axis Cross-Contribution

- Q (QUANTUM):
  - VQE on flat PPI interfaces — hot-spot residue energy decomposition
  - cryptic pocket discovery via quantum-enhanced MD sampling
  - α/β/π hot-spot residue calc (Trp/Tyr/Arg energetics)
- W (WEAVE):
  - peptide-stapled (i, i+4 / i, i+7) scaffolds — PPI helix mimetic cross-link to peptide platform
  - antibody mimetic scaffold (DARPin / monobody) — large-interface PPI capture
- V (VIROCAPSID):
  - none direct — capsid axis 는 PPI modulator delivery layer 가 아님 (gene/payload axis)
- RB (RIBOZYME):
  - PPI mRNA modulation research — 5'UTR / IRES PPI hub mRNA targeting
  - aptazyme PPI sensor-actuator
- NB (NANOBOT):
  - PPI fragment-based delivery — sub-100 Da fragment payload via nanocarrier
  - PROTAC / molecular-glue PPI hijack delivery (TPD overlap)

---

## 3. Falsifier Inventory — F-platform-ppi-*-N (12 entries)

- F-platform-ppi-flat-1: flat PPI interface (>800 Å²) 에 small molecule 결합 ≥10 nM 도달 실패 → undruggable 회귀
- F-platform-ppi-hotspot-2: VQE hot-spot calc 가 mutagenesis ΔΔG 와 r > 0.7 미달 시 quantum advantage falsify
- F-platform-ppi-cryptic-3: MD 로 발견한 cryptic pocket 이 crystal/cryo-EM 으로 재현되지 않으면 artifact
- F-platform-ppi-mdm2-4: 신규 MDM2-p53 inhibitor 가 idasanutlin 대비 selectivity (MDM4 cross) 개선 실패
- F-platform-ppi-menin-5: revumenib / ziftomenib 후속 menin 약물이 escape mutation (M327I 등) 극복 실패
- F-platform-ppi-bcl2-6: navitoclax-class BCL-XL inhibitor 의 thrombocytopenia 회피 실패
- F-platform-ppi-checkpoint-7: oral PD-1/PD-L1 small molecule 이 항체 대비 ORR ≥50% 도달 실패
- F-platform-ppi-aggreg-8: α-syn / tau / TDP-43 aggregation PPI inhibitor 가 in-vivo seeding assay 에서 ≥50% 감소 실패
- F-platform-ppi-staple-9: stapled peptide 가 cellular permeability (PAMPA/Caco-2) 통과 실패
- F-platform-ppi-allo-10: allosteric PPI modulator 가 orthosteric 대비 selectivity advantage 실패
- F-platform-ppi-reactivate-11: APR-246-class mutant-p53 reactivator 가 WT-p53 toxicity 회피 실패
- F-platform-ppi-fragment-12: fragment-based PPI screening hit rate < 0.1% (NMR/SPR) 시 platform 비효율

